
---

### 📦 `.gitignore`
```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

# Virtual Environments
.venv/
env/
ENV/

# Data & Models (тяжёлые артефакты, хранятся локально)
data/
models/
*.parquet
*.pkl
*.joblib
*.pth
*.onnx
*.h5
*.bin
*.model

# IDE & Editors
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Jupyter & Streamlit
.ipynb_checkpoints/
.streamlit/

# Logs & Runtime
logs/
*.log
status.json
.cache/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/

# Environment & Secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.secret
*.key

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.tmp
*.bak

# Python distribution
dist/
*.egg-info
*.egg